Package: temporalCPSA
Title: Cross-Population Survival Analysis via Temporal Molecular Profiles
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Nicole", "Tignor", email = "nicole.tignor@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Nicole Tignor
Maintainer: Nicole Tignor <nicole.tignor@gmail.com>
Description: Framework for both manuscript reproduction and reusable cross-population survival analysis via temporal molecular profiles. The package supports TMP generation, tumor-normal trajectory comparison, trajectory visualization and divergence analysis, multi-omic age-class clustering, and downstream survival modeling including Cross-Population Survival Analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
